comments: Jokic (DEN) briefly brings his arms behind his body and the contact with Butler (MIA) in the post is marginal.
Adebayo (MIA) legally contests Murray's (DEN) perimeter jump shot attempt.
Jokic (DEN) and Adebayo (MIA) engage and disengage away from the ball and the contact is marginal.
Adebayo (MIA) establishes himself in Caldwell-Pope's (DEN) path and marginal contact occurs as the two come together during the pick.
Jokic (DEN) places and removes his hand from Adebayo's (MIA) arm and the contact is marginal as Adebayo sets the pick.
Adebayo (MIA) establishes himself in a wide screening position and firms up into Caldwell-Pope (DEN), which dislodges the defender as he is attempting to move over the pick.
Jokic (DEN) legally contests Herro's (MIA) perimeter jump shot attempt.
Brown (DEN) slightly extends his arms into Butler (MIA) as he jumps for the rebound, but it does not impact his rebounding opportunity.
Lowry (MIA) brings his arm around Murray (DEN) and marginal contact occurs that Murray is able to play on through.
Strus (MIA) initiates contact with Murray's (DEN) body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Adebayo (MIA) is in Murray's (DEN) path when he firms up on his left foot and marginal contact occurs as Murray fights over the pick.
Jokic (DEN) legally contests Adebayo's (MIA) jump shot attempt.
Murray (DEN) and Lowry (MIA) mutually engage and disengage during the rebounding opportunity and the contact is marginal.
Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in Herro's (MIA) path and marginal contact occurs as Herro goes over the pick.
Herro (MIA) rests his hand on Murray's (DEN) side and marginal contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Adebayo (MIA) brings his right arm out and marginal contact occurs with Jokic (DEN) during the inbounds pass.
Butler (MIA) firms up on his left foot and avoids delivering contact to Caldwell-Pope (DEN), who goes over the screen.

Caldwell-Pope (DEN) and Lowry (MIA) engage and disengage as they move towards Adebayo (MIA) and the contact is marginal. After the disengage, Caldwell-Pope continues into Adebayo and dislodges him from his position on the floor.
Jokic (DEN) briefly places and removes his arms from Adebayo's (MIA) sides and the contact is marginal.
Butler (MIA) establishes himself in Caldwell-Pope's (DEN) path and marginal contact occurs as Caldwell-Pope (DEN) moves into the screen.
Herro (MIA) steps his left foot onto the sideline and out of bounds after receiving the pass. Possession should have been awarded to Denver.
Gordon (DEN) legally contests Herro's (MIA) jump shot attempt.
Adebayo (MIA) briefly clasps and releases Jokic's (DEN) left arm during the rebounding opportunity and the contact is marginal.
Jokic (DEN) brings his arm towards the ball and incidental arm contact occurs with Butler (MIA) after the offensive player taps the rebound away from the basket.
Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in Strus' (MIA) path and marginal contact occurs as Jokic releases to roll towards the basket.
Strus (MIA) lightly brushes Murray's (DEN) side during the drive and the contact is marginal.
Strus (MIA) legally contests Murray's (DEN) perimeter jump shot attempt.
Jokic (DEN) initiates arm contact with Adebayo (MIA) that affects his driving shot attempt.
Murray (DEN) establishes himself in Herro's (MIA) path and marginal contact occurs as they come together during the screen.
Herro (MIA) commits a take foul on Caldwell-Pope (DEN).
Adebayo (MIA) firms up on his left foot but turns his body towards Caldwell-Pope (DEN), which dislodges the defender as he attempts to get around the screen.
